{"type":null,"faqId":33558,"title":"充电时手机发热如何处理","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机充电时候发热是正常现象。建议在充电的时候避免长期使用手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请不要充电时将手机放在床上或保温性能好的环境中，充电的热量无法散开会导致温度增加。充电时手机要放在桌面等散热良好的地方。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">华为手机为了提升您体验，使用较大容量的电池和较大输出能力的2A充电器。这样带来了更短的充电时间，但是也会带来一定程度的发热。所有的体验的提升都是建立在确保安全使用的基础之上，所以请放心使用。如果你的手机充电时热感明显，建议您把手机恢复出厂设置或者升级到最新的软件版本。\"</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8278","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748655000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":230,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"充电,发热","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}